  "rawHTML": "<p>发表于：9/30/2023</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>想回国养老？\n绿卡、公民怎么选？<br>四大重点帮你理清思路</p>\t\t\t\t\n\t\t<p>最近有越来越多的客户来问咨询：“我现在人在美国，有绿卡，想着以后回国养老，该怎么规划？”<br />有的是年轻时求学深造移民过来，如今觉得国内生活更热闹，想回去照顾父母，安享退休生活；也有的是来美国帮子女带小孩的，现在孙辈大了，想回国享清福。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">如果你也是这样想的，那接下来这几件事，千万要提前规划好!</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"8192\" height=\"5462\" src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-neil-ni-2148510469-31772145.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-neil-ni-2148510469-31772145.jpg 8192w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-neil-ni-2148510469-31772145-300x200.jpg 300w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-neil-ni-2148510469-31772145-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-neil-ni-2148510469-31772145-768x512.jpg 768w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-neil-ni-2148510469-31772145-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/pexels-neil-ni-2148510469-31772145-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 8192px) 100vw, 8192px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEnvelope\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M464 64H48C21.49 64 0 85.49 0 112v288c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h416c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48V112c0-26.51-21.49-48-48-48zm0 48v40.805c-22.422 18.259-58.168 46.651-134.587 106.49-16.841 13.247-50.201 45.072-73.413 44.701-23.208.375-56.579-31.459-73.413-44.701C106.18 199.465 70.425 171.067 48 152.805V112h416zM48 400V214.398c22.914 18.251 55.409 43.862 104.938 82.646 21.857 17.205 60.134 55.186 103.062 54.955 42.717.231 80.509-37.199 103.053-54.947 49.528-38.783 82.032-64.401 104.947-82.653V400H48z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tExternal-link-square-alt\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg viewBox=\"0 0 448 5